%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu-Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-li%C3%AAn/poem-ZUEg1F9gYr2ZCKNuoPgxpA">Nghệ Tĩnh văn thân điếu Phan Đình Phùng đối liên - 乂靜文紳弔潘廷逢對聯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/Th%E1%BA%A7n-Ph%C3%B9-h%E1%BA%A3i-m%C3%B4n-l%E1%BB%AF-th%E1%BB%A9/poem-WLd9ZKP-JqqT6j5K_0bpYA">Thần Phù hải môn lữ thứ - 神浮海門旅次</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-C%E1%BB%A7ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0u-V%C5%A9-T%C3%ADch/poem-6JYN5fBBVDVoNb2s0x1KIg">Tống Lưu Vũ Tích - 送劉禹錫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-C%E1%BB%A7ng/author-qI9UHMMflLE3z07EmEsamw">Đậu Củng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%A1-L%C3%A3m/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Uy-Linh-Lang-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-zPmB7IVWtFNCeIwQTv1REA">Vịnh Uy Linh Lang tự - 詠威靈郎祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%A1-L%C3%A3m/author-9ppkdEWSUlq0gOg71v0QIQ">Trần Bá Lãm</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
